description:
Texas Flip and Move - Season 2, Episode 6




The Snows Make Over a Duplex with a Bird Theme

Donna and Toni buy a duplex in a neighborhood that is being completely redeveloped. They decide the house will sell best if they turn it into a single-family home. Their design inspiration is a whimsical bird theme because the house originally came from Bird Street.




Original Air Date: 23-Oct-2015
